- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of relational learning in policy evaluation, policy improvement, and reward learning, which are all sub-fields of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on visual imitation learning from video demonstrations, which is a sub-field of computer vision. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper evaluates the proposed method in a challenging locomotion task, which is a common problem in robotics. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of the proposed method for policy evaluation and improvement, which are important topics in systems and control.
